rohit, moderated by Rohan Salvi.\u00a0<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b423320 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b423320\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bc9f87 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"9bc9f87\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/F0IA5IP1DnI&quot;,&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2398baf e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2398baf\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c536b21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c536b21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Watch this virtual round table session where we feature esteemed industry leaders\u00a0Alok Khanna, Manoj Agarwal, and Vijay Purohit, moderated by Rohan Salvi.\u00a0<\/p><p>The discussion will center on the transformative role of Master Data Management (MDM) and emerging technologies in asset-intensive industries. With a focus on digital transformation and data-led leadership, the panel will delve into practical strategies, real-world challenges, and the future of MDM.<\/p><p><strong>Key Takeaways from the Webinar<\/strong><\/p><p>1. <strong>Leadership and Strategy for Digital Transformation<\/strong>: Discover how balancing innovation with compliance, clear risk management strategies, and stakeholder alignment enable successful adoption of technologies like AI and Industry 4.0.<\/p><p>2. <strong>Data and Technology for Sustainability and Scalability<\/strong>: Learn how harmonizing master data and integrating AI revolutionizes MDM processes, supports scaling during mergers, and helps achieve environmental and sustainability goals.<\/p><p>3. <strong>Overcoming Challenges for Seamless Integration<\/strong>: Understand how addressing legacy systems and fostering collaboration empowers organizations to thrive in a data-driven, rapidly evolving technological landscape.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d60456 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0d60456\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-185f934 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"185f934\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Meet The Speakers<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3dcca5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d3dcca5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d908a9c e-con-full pointer e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d908a9c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8657c12 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8657c12\" 