eel production. With over 27 years of experience, Manoj specializes in finance and digital transformation, having implemented ERP systems like SAP and JD Edwards.<\/p><p>A Chartered Accountant, he previously served as Head of IT at HPCL-Mittal Energy and has expertise in emerging technologies like RPA, IIOT, and analytics. His approach focuses on delivering business value through technology.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c212e70 e-con-full pointer e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c212e70\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e9e5be elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8e9e5be\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"372\" height=\"479\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/Alok-Khanna.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-25154\" alt=\"Alok Khanna\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/Alok-Khanna.png 372w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/Alok-Khanna-233x300.png 233w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/Alok-Khanna-150x193.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-440ee5e elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"440ee5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-bo