s the UK, US, Europe, and India.<\/p><p>Vijay has led ERP transformations, post-merger integrations, and digital innovation projects, leveraging AI, automation, and process mining. At Holcim, he oversees 150+ resources, driving IT operations, cloud migration, and customer-centric digital solutions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Digital Transformation &amp; Data-led Leadership in Asset Intensive Industries Watch this virtual round table session where we feature esteemed industry leaders\u00a0Alok Khanna, Manoj Agarwal, and Vijay Purohit, moderated by Rohan Salvi.\u00a0 https:\/\/youtu.be\/F0IA5IP1DnI Watch this virtual round table session where we feature esteemed industry leaders\u00a0Alok Khanna, Manoj Agarwal, and Vijay Purohit, moderated by Rohan Salvi.\u00a0 The [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":25452,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"elementor_header_footer","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[72],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-25110","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-events"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25110","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25110"}],"version-history":[{"count":116,"href":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25110\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":34029,"href":"https:\/\/www.verdant